"{\"uid\": \"mysuncoast.com-2024-08-07-stephen-nedoroscik-lands-sarasota-two-time-olympic-medalist\", \"text\": \"SARASOTA, Fla. (WWSB) - After a few weeks in Paris, France, Stephen Nedoroscik returned to Sarasota on Tuesday night, where he was welcomed home by family, friends, and fans.  Although he is from Worcester, Massachusetts, he has been training  at EVO Gymnastics in Sarasota for two years.  Nedoroscik, who focuses on one sole event at Olympics, helped the U.S. Men's Gymnastics Team win a bronze medal. This was the first team medal for the US men's gymnastics team in 16 years.  Copyright 2024 WWSB. All rights reserved.\"}"